definitions.definition: Of or relating to the reign of Queen Victoria from 1837 to 1901, or that period .
Of or relating to the culture or social conditions of that period.

subdefinitions.definition: In a situation of poverty and social injustice ; Dickensian .
( architecture ) Of the style of architecture or furnishings of that period.

definitions.definition: ( figuratively ) Of or displaying the ( supposed ) ideals or standards of morality of that period; conservative ; also, old-fashioned , out-of-date .

main_definition: Of or relating to the reign of Queen Victoria from 1837 to 1901, or that period .

definitions.definition: Of, from or relating to the state of Victoria , Australia .
examples: Up to 26 properties are believed lost in Victorian bushfires.

main_definition: Of, from or relating to the state of Victoria , Australia .

definitions.definition: Of, from or relating to the city of Victoria , capital of British Columbia , Canada .

main_definition: ( Canada ) Of, from or relating to the city of Victoria , capital of British Columbia , Canada .
